ygData.messageBody:
The Tenticle Whip is a nice low level magic weapon, but its far from being the best, just wait a few levels, hunt around in Najena for a while, then you'll find a really awsome 1h slash weapon.....the Barbed Leather Whip, damage 7 delay 27 :)

Salr D'Taynkk
Dark Warrior of The Kith
Veeshan

>>> "Zwanenburg, John" <ZWANENJ@...> 5.14.99 10:45:29 AM >>>
From: "Zwanenburg, John" <ZWANENJ@...>


Well i wouldnt go so far as to say its awesome for EXP....it has its
ups and downs, ups being places like the snake pits...which are good for exp
around level 9 or 10, but Bb also has THE WORST trains i have ever seen,
they can get pretty nasty at times. i guess im just used to Befallen, in my
opinion its the best dungeon to go to before you hit level 20 or so. After
that people should go check out Najena. you can get possibly the BEST 1h
slashing weapon i have seen there. The tentacle whip. Its speed is amazing
and damage is killer as well, pus its magical.
